## Third-Party Services

This project integrates with the following third-party services:

- **Supabase**: Database and authentication services (https://supabase.com)
- **Paystack**: Payment processing for Ghana (https://paystack.com)
- **Google Speech Recognition**: Voice recognition services
- **Expo**: React Native development platform (https://expo.dev)

Please refer to their respective terms of service and privacy policies.

## Ghana Market Focus

This application is specifically designed for the Ghana market with:
- Ghana Cedis (GHS) currency support
- Ghanaian accent optimization
- Local payment methods (Mobile Money)
- Cultural design elements

Built with ❤️ for Ghana's digital commerce future.

